By: Swami Ramdas
---
God is preparing you to receive the nectar of Ananda. If you get it
without the proper preparation to stand it, your mind and body will be
shattered to pieces. So He is gradually preparing you and when He
knows that you are ready to receive Him, then He comes to you in all
His glory.
